data.description: Absolutely Adorable 3 Bed, 2 Bath Home on 3.1 Acres! Zoned AG. Bring the Toys and Animals! 24x40 Outbuilding/Workshop Built in 2021 comes equipped with a 10,000 LB Lift, Compressor and is Insulated! Shop roller doors are approx. 12x16 and 9x8. Additional smaller shed is 14x24. Primary Yard is Fenced! Electric Gate at Entrance. Two other metal gates behind house lead to back of property. New Roof in 2022! New Pool Pump! Newer Well! Newer A/C! Newer Water Treatment System! All New Interior & Exterior Paint! New Screen on Cage around Pool!  Interior Features include Updated Kitchen!! New Granite countertops and Cabinets! Newer Appliances! This was an FPL Built Smart Home! Wood Burning Fireplace! Washer and Dryer staying for the convenience of the new Buyer! Enjoy the Myakkahatchee Park nearby for Riding Horses, Biking, Jogging, Picnics and Nature Trails! Beautiful Wildlife Surrounds the Neighborhood! Come Expecting to leave Happy!
